Package fasdpd

Class PriorityList<T>

java.lang.Object
fasdpd.PriorityList<T>
Type Parameters:
T - A class that implements Comparable interface.
public class PriorityList<T>
extends java.lang.Object
PriorityList is a kind of list that stores values until a maximum quantity. When this quantity is reached, the new values can displace older if they had a greater priority. Priority is given by natural order. Object stored in this list must implement comparable interface.
